1 tran sferred, the original royalty allocated to that property shall
2 be divided in an amount proportional to the amount of each owner's
3 property that lies within the radius, calculated as a fraction of
4 the total original property area within the radius.
5 B. This section shall only apply to the construction or
6 expansion of wind energy facilities constructed or expanded after
7 the effective date of this act.
8 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2025.
